## Lingui

TO ADD A TRANSLATION
1. Add a <Trans>placeholder text</Trans> element
2. execute: npm run extract
3. Insert the translations in locales/{locale}/messages.po 
4. Execute npm run compile


TO ADD LANGUAGES see: 
_app.tsx
next.config.js
.linguirc

npm run compile